metrics_conclusion: Thunder has higher complexity than the average song  in terms Chord-Bass Melody.
key_conclusion:
Thunder is written in the key of C Major.  

According to the Theorytab database, it is the most common key in all of popular music. 

See the C Major Cheat Sheet for popular chords, chord progressions, downloadable midi files and more!

metadata.editComments: If the Imagine Dragons version is here, why not this one too? Lol btw I didn't put it in G Mixolydian, a aeolian or F Lydian because the vocals don't hit those notes much, but mostly C. That's why I kept it in C Major even though that chord doesn't appear much; this so that when forcibly turned into A Major it doesn't sound even more minor (f#m).
